WEBVTT

00:02.585 --> 00:04.939
Hey, no, nothing strange
about it at all.

00:04.963 --> 00:06.315
I always travel 6000 miles

00:06.339 --> 00:07.900
to visit casual acquaintances.

00:07.924 --> 00:09.151
You can't be jealous.

00:09.175 --> 00:10.611
No, I'm not. You told me

00:10.635 --> 00:12.655
nothing happened between you
and Allison last summer.

00:12.679 --> 00:15.574
I believe you. The fact that she's coming all the
way from England doesn't mean anything anyway.

00:15.598 --> 00:18.452
Julia, she's coming to
check out Berkeley.

00:18.476 --> 00:20.496
- That's it. - Yeah, I know, and
maybe she'll get accepted.

00:20.520 --> 00:22.373
And maybe she'll
live across the bay.

00:22.397 --> 00:23.833
Wouldn't that just be ducky?

00:23.857 --> 00:25.334
Right, right.

00:25.358 --> 00:28.212
We're putting her up
as a favor to her dad.

00:28.236 --> 00:30.163
That's the whole story.

00:30.196 --> 00:31.674
Anyways, Allie is not somebody...

00:31.698 --> 00:34.135
So now it's "Allie"? Allie.
That's cute.

00:34.159 --> 00:35.460
You call her Allie?

00:37.495 --> 00:38.764
Thurber food.

00:38.788 --> 00:41.642
I need a new name for myself.
You know, a hip name.

00:41.666 --> 00:44.510
I mean, does "Sarah Reeves" sound like
the lead singer in a hot band? No.

00:44.544 --> 00:46.272
You need something along the
lines of "Courtney Love."

00:46.296 --> 00:47.523
Exactly.

00:47.547 --> 00:50.943
Yeah. Like... Like
Felicia Luscious.

00:50.967 --> 00:52.518
Ha! Yeah.

00:52.594 --> 00:53.770
No.

00:53.803 --> 00:55.156
No. No.

00:55.180 --> 00:56.449
I'm sorry.

00:56.473 --> 01:00.193
I'm sorry for bothering you. Are
you Shirley Kaplan's daughter?

01:00.935 --> 01:02.111
Who?

01:03.438 --> 01:04.706
Wow, I guess not.

01:04.730 --> 01:06.834
You just look like this woman
who's in the PTA with me.

01:06.858 --> 01:08.284
And your voice too.

01:08.318 --> 01:10.787
Well, I'm sorry. My mistake.

01:11.571 --> 01:13.716
Wait a minute. What did
you say her name was?

01:13.740 --> 01:15.792
Oh, no, nothing. Never mind.

01:17.410 --> 01:18.586
Shut up, Claud.

